    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong> to a low heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a splash of <strong>milk</strong></p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and mash until smooth – this is your <strong>mash</strong></p>",
