    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Dutch-style beef hachee stew</strong> over the <strong>mash</strong> with the <strong>braised</strong> <strong>red</strong> <strong>cabbage</strong> to the side</p><p>Discard the <strong>bay leaf[ves]</strong> and <strong>studded onion</strong></p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
